{"tid":2359544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市區氣溫最低6°C　市民未懼寒流清晨游冬泳","createTime":"2021-01-09T03:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T04:32:16.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"439a69b2d32511db01cde8ad295c6c98af0db592","tid":2359544,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210109/photo/bkn-20210109074248470-0109_00822_001_01p.jpg?20210109092732\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210109%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210109074248470-0109_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20210109092732&h=b76a2e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民未懼寒流跳落水中暢泳。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<br />\n寒冷天氣及霜凍警告生效下，今日(9日)清晨市區氣溫錄得約攝氏6至8度，有多名市民未懼寒風，前往紅磡海濱花園對開晨泳。他們換上一身泳裝後不畏嚴寒，在寒風中仍撲通跳落水中暢泳。泳客蒙先生表示，十多年來每日都風雨不改到來晨泳，覺得今日天氣很冷，水溫亦比平日較低。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210109/photo/bkn-20210109074248470-0109_00822_001_02p.jpg?20210109092732\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210109%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210109074248470-0109_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20210109092732&h=ef748758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有市民到紅磡海濱花園對開游冬泳。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210109/photo/bkn-20210109074248470-0109_00822_001_03p.jpg?20210109092732\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210109%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210109074248470-0109_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20210109092732&h=6e51e27f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泳客蒙先生表示今天水温比平日較低。(胡德威攝)"},{"pid":"e908235017baf4e6a2164acc913a8ad4facb06e2","tid":2359544,"uid":152147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:56:25.000Z","msg":"599I<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a7beee2567dafd0e6b9beacf162112849cb418","tid":2359544,"uid":125357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T0